reviewText: Daughter begged me for this and I gave it to her as a reward for doing well in school and being helpful.

Christmas present for granddaughter. She loves it, so I love it. Speedy delivery, fair price, dvd in good condition.
Thank you.
I bought this for my son since he really enjoyed the books. He seems to love the movie and has even shared it, along with the books, with his class.
This cartoon is so intelligently written that I actually encourage my kids to watch it (over the others) and I gladly watch it with them!
